      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds nice, but it doesn't really fix the feeling of being useless. Most people seem to have a purpose or a way to contribute to the survival of the species, but I just feel like a dead end. Like my line just stops here and doesn't add anything to the bigger picture. Isn't that what evolution is about? Trimming away the things that don't serve a purpose?",
